sentences: The SBSTA addressed any other matters in Plenary on Friday, 6 June.
Several Parties suggested SBSTA express support for the World Conference on Climate Change to be held in Moscow from 29 September to 3 October 2003.
Chair Thorgeirsson said he would hold informal consultations on this issue and prepare draft conclusions.
The SBSTA adopted draft conclusions with a minor amendment on Friday, 13 June.
